    <item>
      <title>埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）下周将访问中央情报机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/elon-musk-set-to-visit-central-intelligence-agency-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）将于周一访问中央情报机构，这是通过美国政府的间谍机构巡回演出的最新站，引起了一些民主党和情报专家的警报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/elon-musk-set-to-visit-central-intelligence-agency-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 21:22:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上诉法院在援助机构的马斯克战斗中提升了道门限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/appeals-court-lifts-doge-limits-at-aid-agency-amid-musk-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院将限制埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）和与其政府效率部项目相关的人们可以在监督外国人道主义援助的美国机构中发挥的作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/appeals-court-lifts-doge-limits-at-aid-agency-amid-musk-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 21:13:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上诉法院说，特朗普可以解雇两个机构负责人。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/appeals-court-will-let-trump-fire-independent-agency-heads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）可以解雇两个独立机构的成员，华盛顿的联邦上诉法院裁定，裁定了总统为重塑美国政府的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/appeals-court-will-let-trump-fire-independent-agency-heads</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 19:34:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国援助机构将于7月1日与国务院合并</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/usaid-set-to-merge-with-state-department-on-july-1-agency-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周五发出的国会通知，美国国际发展机构将在7月1日之前合并到国务院，援助机构剩余人员的剩余人员将被解雇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/usaid-set-to-merge-with-state-department-on-july-1-agency-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 18:31:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划主持萨尔瓦多的布克利四月访问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-plans-to-host-el-salvador-s-bukele-at-white-house-in-april</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据布克勒办公室称，唐纳德·特朗普总统将于下个月在华盛顿接待萨尔瓦多总统纳耶布·布克利，此前中美洲领导人同意监禁数百名涉嫌委内瑞拉帮派成员被驱逐出美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-plans-to-host-el-salvador-s-bukele-at-white-house-in-april</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 16:03:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普，卡尼谈论新政，加拿大当选后的计划会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-carney-talk-amid-trade-spat-plan-to-meet-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他与加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）进行了交谈，两人将在加拿大当选后开会，这在附近的盟友和主要贸易伙伴之间发动了加剧的关税战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-carney-talk-amid-trade-spat-plan-to-meet-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 15:14:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
